		"description": "<p>Your combination of strict training and brutal wrath makes you difficult to escape from and worse to fight. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your movement speed increases by 10 feet.</li>\n<li>You have a climb speed equal to your movement speed.</li>\n<li>If you hit with two unarmed attacks in the same turn, you can use your reaction to rend the target, dealing an additional 2d6 points of slashing damage.</li>\n<li>While you are raging, your senses sharpen. You have advantage on Perception checks while raging.</li>\n<li>Half your adept levels count as berserker levels for the purpose of the Crushing Blows feature.</li>\n</ul>",
